m\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/08\/08\/supplication-better-gold-silver\/","url_meta":{"origin":35595,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Words of prayer better than gold and silver","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 8, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Shaddad ibn Aws reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you see people amassing gold and silver, then amass these words: O Allah, I ask You for firmness in the matter and determination upon guidance. I ask You for gratitude over Your blessings, I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1738,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/08\/allah-you-are-as-praised-yourself\/","url_meta":{"origin":35595,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: O Allah, You are as You praised Yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: One night in bed, I missed the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, so I looked for him and my hand touched his feet while he was in prostration. They were raised, and the Prophet was saying, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in Your pleasure\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21935,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/15\/comprehensive-and-concise-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":35595,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Use comprehensive and concise supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered my room while I was praying and I was slow to take care of his need. The Prophet said, \u201cO Aisha, you must use comprehensive and concise supplications.\u201d When I finished, I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/tashahhud-fi-hajjah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35595,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Testifying to faith in prayer and in need","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught us to bear witness to faith in prayer and to bear witness to faith in times of need. Bearing witness in prayer is to say, \u201cGreetings are for Allah, as are prayers and pure things.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18154,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/17\/dua-protection-with-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35595,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Protect me from my enemies with Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would supplicate, saying, \u201cO Allah,